snippet.title: Citadel: Forged With Fire | Coming to PS4 & Xbox One November 1, 2019
snippet.description:
Citadel: Forged With Fire is coming to PlayStation 4 and Xbox One November 1, 2019. The game will be available digitally or at retail!

PRE-ORDER: https://www.citadelthegame.com/pre-order
